(18, 'page', 'get-started', 'Get Started', NULL, '', '<section class="getstarted-area">\r\n<div class="container">\r\n<div class="hed">\r\n<h2>Get <span>Started</span></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="get__lft get__rgt col-sm-6 bdr-next">\r\n<div class="hed clrhm">\r\n<h3>GET STARTED AS A HAMMER FIT <span>ATHLETE!</span></h3>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="get__pdf col-sm-4 mb20 pl0"><a href="https://www.hammerfit.net/MAXFTT.pdf"><img atl="maxftt_mag.jpg" src="https://www.hammerfit.net/front/images/maxftt_mag.jpg" style="width: 188px; height: 300px;" /></a>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="cont col-sm-8 pr0">\r\n<p>Get started today shaping your Physique into the Physique of your DREAMS! At Hammer Fit, we believe the real you, the one that you always imagined looking back at you in the mirror is not only there waiting for you, it is very much within your reach to have NOW!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Not only will we help you reach your goal, we will help you understand how to keep that Physique by guiding and teaching you our highly effective training and nutrition techniques.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="http://www.hammerfit.net/MAXFTT.pdf">Download PDF</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="cont col-sm-12 p0">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-2eb604c6-9b3a-942b-3a60-f75bdabed356"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">The first step To star as a Hammer Fit is to download the MaxFTT training guide This guide is the basis for what we do We working hard, incredibly hard and as such nutrition supplementation are critical to your success. Learn the WHY&#39;s&#39; This is where we operate.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At Hammer Fit, we work in the WHY ZONE, the area where we believe it is critical for you to understand the basis for the mehtods we deploy. Understand why something is important to you! Having the information &nbsp;about critical reasons behind what you are doing only propels you to want to do it with all your heart. When heart and passion collide, success is only the next logical step!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Whether you are a Bodybuilding Competitor where you want to display your incredible physique to the world for sport, merely looking to obtain the best physique of your life or just wanting to shed a couple pounds and tone up, Hammer Fit and Hammer Fit Ambassadors will make YOUR goal THEIR goal!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>So let&#39;s get working togther. Download your FREE copy of MaxFTT today and have the opportunity to understand our theories. Take the time to know us and then once you are ready to HAMMER that body into the physique you want, then get started on your profile and JOIN OUR TEAM!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="strong">Proceed to the&nbsp;<a href="signup">Login</a>&nbsp;Screen and Apply to be an Athlete today!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="get__rgt col-sm-6">\r\n<div class="hed clrhm">\r\n<h3>GET STARTED AS A HAMMER FIT <span>COACH!</span></h3>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="cont">\r\n<p>Are you a Fitness Competitor that always wanted to jump into the realm of helping others attain their fitness dreams? Are you someone that has always had the calling to see other succeed and their success feels like your success? Are you a person that loves people, is down to earth, humble, respectful to others goals and can align yourself with the goals of others as if they were your own? Did you always want to learn to coach others but just didn&#39;t know where to start?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you answered yes to this series of questions, then Hammer Fit may be the perfect home for you. Hammer Fit is all about the Athlete. We are here to serve the Athlete to the best that we can and we are looking for good people that want to excel with us in the industry.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nThat being said, to Hammer Fit, remember you are also an Athlete! That means when you Join Hammer Fit as a Coach, you become part of the family and as such, reap the rewards for joining a great growing team of people that operate with heart.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nOur mission is to provide impeccable service at a reasonable rate. We want to give all people and Athletes the opportunity to have someone in their corner that cares about them and wants to see them excel at a very fair cost.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nAs a Hammer Fit Ambassador, you will coach people the Hammer Fit way. You will learn the proven techniques that have time and again produced amazing results. You will be required to teach and use these and only these techniques. Standards must be followed at all times to ensure consistent approach across the United States as we grow. Very high communication standards are required at all times. We love our athletes and as such, we require you communicate promptly to any questions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nAs support for our strong beliefs and creating a company of loving and caring Athletes helping Athletes, Hammer Fit will award you a very lucrative payment package that includes high rate commission on all fees, retail sales on upcoming products and merchandise purchased by your Athletes (NO lame code for people to input that they never use). We believe we are creating a company where all participants are fairly rewarded for advancing the company, not another one of those companies giving you their own product as payment (there are enough of these out there&#39;&#39;). If you want to help others, have the protection of a strong brand and company behind you, earn very fair income while you do so and grow with a fast growing company, then apply today!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="strong">Proceed to the <a href="signup">Login</a> Screen and Apply to be an Coach today!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n', '', 'Get Started', '', '', NULL, '2017-07-25 08:59:55', 1, 0, NULL, NULL),
